<script>
    $(document).ready(function(){
        var f1 = FormUtil.getField("valor");
        var number = FormUtil.getValue("valor");
        
        console.log("1"+number);
        if(number != null && number !== ""){
           
            number = number.replaceAll('NaN', "0");
            console.log("2"+number);
            
            number = number.replaceAll('.', "");
            console.log(number);
            
            number = number.replaceAll('€', "");
            console.log("3"+ number);
            
            number = number.replaceAll('Eur', "");
            console.log("4" + number);
            
            number = number.replaceAll('EUR', "");
            console.log("5"+ number);
            
            number = number.replaceAll(',', '.');
            
            let num = new Intl.NumberFormat('pt-PT', { style: 'currency', currency: 'EUR' }).format(number);
        
            num = num.replace(/\s/g, '.');
            num = num.replaceAll('.€', ' EUR');
            
            $(f1).val(num);
        }else{
            //do nothing
        }
    });
</script>
